column5: I'll be travelling from International Falls to just south of Kenora for the Walleye opener on Friday, May 19th.Anybody know of bait stores on that route that will have quality leeches. I'm aware of the Can-Op on the east side of Ft. Francis but would like to avoid going out of my way if possible.Later....Al
If your going through Nestor Falls you could get them at Eastwoods Bait on the south side of town
